<i>noun</i>: 해이 [해ː이] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>해이 [해ː이]</dt><br>
<dd>slackness; laxity; looseness</dd><br>
<dd>긴장이나 지켜야 할 규율 등이 풀려 마음이 느슨함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which one's mind eases due to the release of tension, or a loosening of rules one is expected to follow.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>